WHAT EDUCATIONAL VIDEOS ARE ON PLOOP CHANNEL?
Your child or toddler's favorite kid's toys & cars & cartoon characters learning to count numbers plus we have 3d Chocolate Eggs videos with Fire Trucks, Trains, Toy Construction Machine Vehicles & Puzzles.

We also have Toy review videos with Toy Collections and Construction Vehicles with Pixar cars, Lego toys, Bburago toys, Go gears toys, Brio toys,Alice toys plus Toy Trains and Railways!

By using building blocks to construct structures & toy sets, budding engineers, architects and designers can build towers, bridges & cities. Kids can see how to build hot air Balloons, Jeeps, ATV, 4wd vehicles with iPad mobile app games. Children can watch & learn how to construct with Ploop Channel's English, educational 3d videos & cartoons about machines and construction with Fire Engines, Construction Machine Vehicles & Interactive Puzzles!
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

snippet.title: Toy Unboxing: Max and Ruby open a Twisti Scooter!
snippet.description:
We challenged our Razor Jr. kids to unbox the super cute Twisti scooter. Our cameras captured the silly antics of Max and Ruby as they try to free the toy from its package.Usually a task left to mom or dad, the kids finally succeed and go out for a ride! Check out this adorably cute clip from Razor Jr.!

Also check out how to make Olaf, from Frozen out of a Twisti scooter: http://youtu.be/gBGwRsL2Suo

…And then see the Olaf Twisti scooter in action with Anna (sung by Ruby) performing Do You Want To Build a Snowman: http://youtu.be/I33R72GGgc4

The Twisti toddler ride-on is the cutest bug that invites little movers to take a fun ride. With darling Little Buzz and Lady Buzz bumble bee designs, kids simply have a seat, rest their feet, and they're off – moving the handlebars side-to-side to propel themselves. Twisti's bright eyes follow along, moving back-and-forth for a real bug's eye view! This scooter is designed for 18 months and up (up to 55 pounds.) 

Always wear appropriate safety equipment.  Exercise caution and common sense – do not assume you can easily to everything you may see on a video, because all trick or aggressive riding takes practice and involves increased risks.  Always check local laws regarding use of electric-powered products.

Learn more at: http://www.razor.com/razor-jr/products/razor-jr/twisti/

snippet.title: BEST Kids Makeup Tutorial Unboxing Makeup Kit Unicorn & Mermaid Makeup Brushes Review
snippet.description:
Watch my Best Kids Makeup Lip Gloss Unboxing Review & How to apply lip gloss for beginners Petite 'n Pretty https://youtu.be/9mm4E8i5qus
Tiffany Taylor Makeup Tutorials https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgGrs0LDn9SkKnC6SNAF56nO52FEg5ug0
BEST Kids Makeup Tutorial Unboxing Makeup Kit Unicorn & Mermaid Makeup Brushes Review by Tiffany Taylor Now before everyone gets all worked up YES Tiffany Taylor is only 4…NO…she won’t be wearing this everyday. Yes…she is beautiful the way she is and I tell her that everyday. This make up is JUST FOR FUN, for her DIY LOL Surprise makeovers, for halloween makeup tutorials and kids makeup challenges. I do not like using MY makeup on her so I did some research and found THE BEST REAL SAFE MAKEUP for kids! This makeup beauty kit is perfect for tweens and for girls who are just learning and experimenting with makeup. Let me just say that these makeup brushes are SUPER CUTE! So HAPPY with this makeup and beauty products! Keep reading for full details!
Ammiy Unicorn Makeup Brushes Set Fantasy Makeup Tools With a Cute Iridescent Holographic Carrying Case (Amazon’s Choice) 
These unicorn makeup brushes are cruelty free with nylon hair and handle material plating, plastic. Including 10 different shapes and sizes of brushes. Based on high quality hair, it provides superb ability to hold powder, soft and pleasing for your skin. Best gift for your friends or family members. The handles of the brushes are twisted like a Unicorn Horn in a very pale pearly lilac shade, unique design brush pole shape , to ensure comfortable feel and easy to use. These unicorn brushes Intended for makeup beginner and enthusiasts, the creative possibilities are endless. The unicorn makeup brushes are comfortable to hold with the twisted design on the handles, and very lightweight too. The case they come in helps you to keep them all together and in good condition, and of course, you can take it with you if you're away from home. 
Mermaid Makeup Brush Set Professional Eye Makeup Brushes- Odour free, safe for sensitive skin. Non-shedding, easy to stick powder as well as easy to clean and dry off fast. Popular Mermaid Shape: Bright multi-color gradient premium plastic handles with 3D fish scale will give you an incredible touch feeling and stylish visual feel. Suitable for both professional or individual use. Usage: This mermaid makeup eye brushes are both suitable for applied to liquid, powder or cream cosmetics to produce a flawless eye looks. Ideally for applying, shading and blending products to show your natural beauty. Two gradient color for you to choose. Also the best multipurpose eye brush set to create a perfect smoky eye looks or other eye makeup applications.
SHANY ‘Fix Me Up’ Makeup Kit, Multi by SHANY Cosmetics UNBOXING and REVIEW- This makeup kit is full of vibrant makeup. Grand total of 36 matte or pearl finish eye shadows. Eight lip colors with a semi-glossy finish and applicators. True-to-color and super pigmented makeup that silky soft. SHANY is a member of PETA and products are cruelty free designed by makeup professionals in the U.S.A. This beauty kit is that it is better than any of the “play" makeup I have seen. The colors are very rich and pigmented which is perfect for kids who really want to see the makeup when they look in the mirror. This makeup kit looks more “mature” than play makeup so it is perfect for girls between ages 6 and up (tweens) who wouldn’t want a makeup set for “little kids.” This beauty makeup kit arrived in PERFECT condition and it is packaged well. I also love that it is not long lasting and washes off easily.

snippet.title: Birthday Haul! Nerf Elite and X-Shot Blaster Unboxing and Review
snippet.description:
We're celebrating a birthday on Kids Toys Play, by unboxing some awesome Nerf review and Zuru X-Shot blasters! We've got the Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 and Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack and 2x Xcess sets, and a ton of darts! We even have the new Thomas and Friends trackmaster push along Birthday Celebration train set! Lots to unbox and review on our family friendly channel for kids!

Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack Double Swarm Seeker 0:15
Take down flying targets with X-Shot Flying Bug Attack! Place your bugs onto the motorized launcher, step on the pedal and release it to see bugs soar in the air. Take them down with the exclusive Swarm-Seeker blaster!

KEY FEATURES:

• Real Flying Bug Attack that hover in the air for you to blast down!

• Motorized launcher that works by pressing its button down with your foot so you have your hands free to shot down the bugs!

• Release the pedal and watch your bugs fly through the air. Take them down before they land!

• The Swarm-Seeker is specially tailored for quick fire with its 10 dart capacity magazine so you\'ll have plenty of shots to hit your targets!

Zuru X-Shot 2x Xcess 1:07
With a pull to prime mechanism and a dual dart system firing both discs and darts, from a special rotating double barrel system, your opponent won’t know what hit them!

KEY FEATURES:

• Shoots darts up to 80ft/24m

• 6 Dart Capacity (each) Dual Barrel

• Discs for short range targets

PACK INCLUDES:

1x X-Shot XCESS Blaster

12x X-Shot Foam Darts

Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 2:00
Slam into battle with the double-barreled excellence of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster! This sleek blaster lets you launch 2 Elite Darts at once at targets up to 75 feet away, and the pump-action design lets you pump repeatedly to unleash a steady double stream of darts! Launch up to 8 Elite Darts without reloading! As with most N-STRIKE blasters, the Tactical Rail lets you add most N-STRIKE Tactical Rail accessories (sold separately) for more battle capability. Power up the multishot madness of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster and get ready to dominate with both barrels!

 Thanks for watching, thumbs up if you enjoyed our video!
